之力消耗對方資源</ins></strong><br />\n福建幫同之前鄉黑最大分別係佢地事先已經花咗一大筆資金book酒店，亦都有哂巴絲提供證據<br />\n唔同之前流浮山傳聞<br />\n其實浪費佢地資金，打擊佢地士氣都係一個對抗手法<br />\n<br />\n最後，我地係要嚴防散水黨，亦要深切反思下一步行動點樣升級<br />\n但希望各位巴絲唔好因為運動陷入樽頸位去同爛命黑社會硬碰<br />\n請緊記我地要有勇 同時有謀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日。五。罷買救港</span></span></strong><br />\n罷買運動正式開始<br />\n之前推過罷買,反應唔錯,於是同其他巴打一齊統一搞左星期五,日罷買, 一星期2日, 請幫手集中推以下2個POST<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXM0w4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXM0w4O.jpg&h=6004208b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(和理非全面升級)星期五，日0消費！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436038/page/1</a><br />\n「驚就唔好出街！」BYE BUY DAY 全城罷買投票結果出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436025/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436025/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e6dfafd0ca8746556f6ae6568a68f6f5a4a07262","tid":1438084,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"唔好再屌中計黨"},{"pid":"c5f0b9820fa55c0501e7ec3d9ed1071f2fb9ebfc","tid":1438084,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efecd52686a2151982a0b72f46972b0b11c72e2","tid":1438084,"uid":278288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c15b4da1e559c513d9ddd287f3ef219710df7171","tid":1438084,"uid":199971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ca992177bc3937e24b8ea8731aefc2f9477e08","tid":1438084,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375a6a450b94f949a14b532b6a179819a34fc639","tid":1438084,"uid":199971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"點解成個連登既人都話福建幫會出黎？<br />\n上次元朗又吹到幾百刀手，卒之影都冇，今次北角又吹出棍手？<br />\n你地係咪索野索過龍呀仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":